          <option value="13">Katipunan (LRT-2)</option>
          <option value="14">J.P. Rizal</option>
          <option value="14">Hi-Top Supermarket (F. Castillo)</option>
          <option value="14">Anonas (LRT-2)</option>
          <option value="15">Cubao (Gateway / Aurora Boulevard)</option>
        </select>

        <button
          type="button"
          onclick="calculate(startStation, endStation)"
          class="calculate-button"
        >
          Calculate
        </button>
      </form>
      <hr />

      <div id="fareDisplaySection">
        <div>
          <p class="fare-text-desc">
            Estimated Fare: <span id="text-fare">₱0</span>
          </p>
          <p class="fare-text-desc">
            Estimated Discounted fare: <span id="textDiscount">₱0</span>
          </p>
          <p class="fare-text-desc">
            Estimated Travel Time: <span id="travelTime">0 Minute</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="explanation">
        <h2>How to calculate your Jeepney fare?</h2>
        <ol>
          <li>
            Know the Base Fare
            <ul>
              <li>
                Traditional Jeepneys – Usually ₱13.00 for the first 4 kilometers
              </li>
              <li>
                Modern Jeepneys – Usually ₱14.00 for the first 4 kilometers
              </li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>
            Know the Base Fare
            <ul>
              <li>Traditional Jeepneys - ₱1.80 - ₱2.00 per kilometer</li>
              <li>Modern Jeepneys - ₱2.20 - ₱2.50 per kilometer</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>
            Check for Fare Discounts
            <ul>
              <li>Students, senior citizens, and PWDs get a 20% discount</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>
            Consider Special Cases
            <ul>
              <li>Late-night or special trips might have additional charges</li>
              <li>
                Always bring small bills/coins as drivers may not always have
                change
              </li>
            </ul>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
